==English==
===Noun===
'''[[mist]]s of [[time]]'''
#Any time so long ago that history is no longer clear, as though lost in a mist or [[fog]].

===Quotations===
"Far back in the '''mists of ancient time''', in the great and glorious days of the former Galactic Empire, life was wild, rich and largely tax free."  &mdash; Douglas Adams, ''Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy''